name: Make core memories with Inside Out 2
long_desc: For the first time ever, celebrate the life and music of our friend and The Revolution’s legendary frontman, Prince, by staying at the actual Purple Rain house from the film. Enjoy an intimate tour, groove to some rare Prince songs, and get some sleep in The Kid’s bedroom. Wear your finest purple fits, and when you step into history, feel free to unleash your royal rockstar. Stay tuned.
